@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_olutte(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.91) + ((v1 + 0.05 - tmp + 0.50) * (v0 + 0.38 - v2 + 0.73)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.79)))
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.61) * v1)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((tmp + 0.07 / v1 + 0.11)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(tmp + 0.12) - (v2 + 0.42 * v1 + 0.10)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
